w minutes early to grab a spot. Use posted signage around Santa Clara to navigate any temporary closures.\\\",\\\"lastUpdated\\\":\\\"2025-11-14T19:36:02.813163+00:00\\\"},{\\\"question\\\":\\\"How do I contact the team at A Pet Villa Dog Boarding and Grooming?\\\",\\\"answer\\\":\\\"For reservations, temperament assessments, or party rentals, call (408) 988-3118, and visit http://apetvilla.com/. The concierge team at A Pet Villa Dog Boarding and Grooming typically replies within one business day.\\\",\\\"lastUpdated\\\":\\\"2025-11-14T19:36:02.813163+00:00\\\"}],\\\"source\\\":\\\"static\\\",\\\"listingType\\\":\\\"free\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"ChIJUetlFt7OxokRFqsJSocfz94\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"A Plus Pet Grooming\\\",\\\"businessType\\\":\\\"Dog Park\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"$31\\\",\\\"slug\\\":\\\"a-plus-pet-grooming\\\",\\\"address\\\":\\\"55 Crescent Blvd\\\",\\\"street\\\":\\\"55 Crescent Blvd\\\",\\\"city\\\":\\\"Gloucester City\\\",\\\"state\\\":\\\"NJ\\\",\\\"zipCode\\\":\\\"08030\\\",\\\"full_address\\\":\\\"55 Crescent Blvd, Gloucester City, NJ 08030, USA\\\",\\\"latitude\\\":39.8916248,\\\"longitude\\\":-75.1040242,\\\"googlePlaceId\\\":\\\"ChIJUetlFt7OxokRFqsJSocfz94\\\",\\\"phone\\\":\\\"(856) 742-0007\\\",\\\"website\\\":\\\"https://www.facebook.com/A-PLUS-PET-GROOMING-114184378604900/\\\",\\\"photos\\\":null,\\\"rating\\\":4.7,\\\"reviewCount\\\":168,\\\"openingHours\\\":{\\\"Monday\\\":\\\"Closed\\\",\\\"Tuesday\\\":\\\"9:00 AM – 3:00 PM\\\",\\\"Wednesday\\\":\\\"9:00 AM – 3:00 PM\\\",\\\"Thursday\\\":\\\"9:00 AM – 3:00 PM\\\",\\\"Friday\\\":\\\"9:00 AM – 3:00 PM\\\",\\\"Saturday\\\":\\\"9:00 AM – 3:00 PM\\\",\\\"Sunday\\\":\\\"Closed\\\"},\\\"amenities\\\":{\\\"Onsite services\\\":true,\\\"Indoor facilities\\\":true,\\\"Professional staff\\\":true,\\\"Climate controlled\\\":true,\\\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\\\":true,\\\"Parking available\\\":true,\\\"Easy access\\\":true},\\\"pricing\\\":{\\\"pricingSource\\\":\\\"website\\\",\\\"isFree\\\":fal