roof of current rabies and core vaccinations, a leash for entry and exit, and an ID tag with up-to-date contact info to breeze through check-in at A Pet Villa Dog Boarding and Grooming. Download the waiver from http://apetvilla.com/ and submit your dog profile before your visit.\",\"lastUpdated\":\"2025-11-14T19:36:02.813163+00:00\"},{\"question\":\"How does pricing work at A Pet Villa Dog Boarding and Grooming?\",\"answer\":\"A Pet Villa Dog Boarding and Grooming offers flexible memberships and punch cards so you can tailor visits to your routine. Contact the desk for the latest promotions or multi-dog discounts.\",\"lastUpdated\":\"2025-11-14T19:36:02.813163+00:00\"},{\"question\":\"Which amenities does A Pet Villa Dog Boarding and Grooming offer?\",\"answer\":\"The team rotates toys, agility props, and splash features weekly so repeat visits to A Pet Villa Dog Boarding and Grooming never feel stale. Expect shaded seating, rinse stations, and staff roaming the yards to keep playgroups safe.\",\"lastUpdated\":\"2025-11-14T19:36:02.813163+00:00\"},{\"question\":\"When is A Pet Villa Dog Boarding and Grooming open and where do I park?\",\"answer\":\"Hours rotate with weather and staffing, so call ahead to confirm current play blocks. Street and shared-lot parking is available nearby; arrive a few minutes early to grab a spot. Use posted signage around Santa Clara to navigate any temporary closures.\",\"lastUpdated\":\"2025-11-14T19:36:02.813163+00:00\"},{\"question\":\"How do I contact the team at A Pet Villa Dog Boarding and Grooming?\",\"answer\":\"For reservations, temperament assessments, or party rentals, call (408) 988-3118, and visit http://apetvilla.com/. The concierge team at A Pet Villa Dog Boarding and Grooming typically replies within one business day.\",\"lastUpdated\":\"2025-11-14T19:36:02.813163+00:00\"}],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJUetlFt7OxokRFqsJSocfz94\",\"name\":\"A Plus Pet Grooming\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\